author: Jeremy Jahns
description:
THE CHOSEN follows the story of Jesus, and has been a phenomenon, growing in popularity over the course of its run. We now come to the Last Supper, in which 2 episodes of Season 5 get theatrical releases leading up to Easter. Here are my thoughts on THE CHOSEN: LAST SUPPER - PART ONE

#TheChosen #TheChosenSeries
title: The Chosen: Last Supper (Part One) - Review
